            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "G-7財長將討論對中印實施二級制裁可能性 針對採購俄油",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"G-7財長將討論對中印實施二級制裁可能性 針對採購俄油\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Wnyggs3EebbmjXOhi5D_gQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/426ae050-8fd2-11f0-adf2-3bd2f70371fb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">G-7財長將討論對中印實施二級制裁可能性 針對採購俄油</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
